From: conda-forge <conda-forge@example.com>
Date: Sun, 06 Apr 2025 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add find_package(GTest) in tests/CMakeLists.txt

Since googletest is no longer built via add_subdirectory in 3rdparty,
call find_package(GTest REQUIRED) directly in the tests directory before
nvcv_test_main is defined, ensuring the GTest::gtest and GTest::gmock
imported targets are available in the correct scope.
---
 tests/CMakeLists.txt | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/tests/CMakeLists.txt b/tests/CMakeLists.txt
index 1111111..2222222 100644
--- a/tests/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/tests/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -29,3 +29,7 @@ set(CMAKE_CXX_STANDARD 20)
 enable_testing()

+if(BUILD_TESTS)
+    find_package(GTest REQUIRED)
+endif()
+
 add_library(nvcv_test_main Main.cpp)
